WEBVTT

00:00:13.105 --> 00:00:15.825
Do I… have cancer, Doctor?

00:00:15.905 --> 00:00:18.345
Fortunately, it’s still treatable.

00:00:18.425 --> 00:00:20.225
You need to get better first, okay?

00:00:20.305 --> 00:00:23.705
I'll take you everywhere you want to go.

00:00:23.785 --> 00:00:24.785
I feel like…

00:00:24.865 --> 00:00:27.185
I can touch other people again.

00:00:27.785 --> 00:00:28.945
Sailom…

00:00:29.025 --> 00:00:30.425
Will you be my boyfriend?

00:00:30.505 --> 00:00:31.705
Is it going to be a burden

00:00:32.584 --> 00:00:34.425
to be with a broken man like me?

00:00:36.025 --> 00:00:37.225
We’ll have to find out.

00:01:54.785 --> 00:01:56.705
You look pretty cheerful today.

00:01:58.465 --> 00:02:00.425
The boss sent me for the interest.

00:02:01.225 --> 00:02:02.185
Hand it over.

00:02:02.785 --> 00:02:04.105
Here’s your "interest."

00:02:05.425 --> 00:02:06.225
DinDin!

00:02:06.825 --> 00:02:07.665
Bastard!

00:02:10.985 --> 00:02:11.945
DinDin!

00:02:24.105 --> 00:02:25.465
Don't waste your energy running.

00:02:25.545 --> 00:02:27.345
Just pay up!

00:02:27.425 --> 00:02:29.785
What the hell? I already paid you!

00:02:29.865 --> 00:02:31.785
3,000 wasn’t enough!

00:02:31.865 --> 00:02:33.185
You owe me a million!

00:02:34.465 --> 00:02:36.945
A million?
It was only five hundred thousand.

00:02:37.025 --> 00:02:39.625
Interest piles up when you miss payments.

00:02:39.705 --> 00:02:41.585
That's just business.

00:02:42.265 --> 00:02:43.105
What?!

00:02:43.185 --> 00:02:44.945
You’re just preying on the poor.

00:02:45.025 --> 00:02:48.585
I didn't force you to borrow a dime.

00:02:48.665 --> 00:02:51.345
You all came to me on your own.

00:02:51.425 --> 00:02:54.745
Stop yapping and pay the interest!

00:02:55.385 --> 00:02:56.225
I won’t pay!

00:02:56.825 --> 00:02:58.145
I won’t pay, no matter what!

00:02:58.225 --> 00:02:59.945
You won’t pay?!

00:03:00.625 --> 00:03:01.665
Come here!

00:03:02.545 --> 00:03:03.625
You won’t pay?!

00:03:04.345 --> 00:03:05.665
You won’t pay?!

00:03:07.225 --> 00:03:08.625
How about now?

00:03:13.545 --> 00:03:15.265
Since you can't find the cash…

00:03:16.425 --> 00:03:17.425
Stay still!

00:03:20.025 --> 00:03:22.425
You can pay with something else.

00:03:23.265 --> 00:03:24.345
What are you doing?

00:03:25.065 --> 00:03:26.465
Organs…

00:03:29.225 --> 00:03:30.065
fetch a good price these--

00:03:35.505 --> 00:03:36.305
Hey!

00:03:38.585 --> 00:03:39.665
You want to meddle in this?

00:03:40.385 --> 00:03:42.025
You want to play hero?

00:04:07.945 --> 00:04:08.905
Arg!

00:04:08.985 --> 00:04:10.025
Kill them both!

00:04:10.105 --> 00:04:11.385
Here you go!

00:04:23.625 --> 00:04:24.865
Gentle!

00:04:30.465 --> 00:04:31.665
Who were those guys?

00:04:34.505 --> 00:04:36.065
My loan sharks' goons.

00:04:39.745 --> 00:04:41.505
You shouldn't have gotten involved.

00:04:42.945 --> 00:04:45.305
Your business is my business too.

00:04:47.705 --> 00:04:48.745
Uh…

00:04:50.145 --> 00:04:51.185
I mean…

00:04:53.185 --> 00:04:54.705
because you're my employee.

00:04:56.705 --> 00:04:57.865
Yeah?

00:05:02.785 --> 00:05:05.785
Why did they beat you up so badly?

00:05:07.505 --> 00:05:08.905
They scammed my mom.

00:05:10.785 --> 00:05:15.145
At first, they said no interest.

00:05:16.145 --> 00:05:18.865
Then it jumped to 20%.

00:05:20.465 --> 00:05:23.305
The principal was only a few hundred
thousand, but it never goes down.

00:05:23.825 --> 00:05:25.625
So, you have to have many jobs.

00:05:27.145 --> 00:05:28.025
Yes.

00:05:29.385 --> 00:05:32.185
My mom put this house up as collateral.

00:05:34.745 --> 00:05:38.385
My grandma’s shop had to close down
because those bastards kept harassing us.

00:05:39.385 --> 00:05:44.185
I promised myself I’d do whatever it takes

00:05:45.945 --> 00:05:48.225
to save this home.

00:05:51.145 --> 00:05:52.065
DinDin,

00:05:53.985 --> 00:05:55.545
I believe you can do it.

00:06:12.745 --> 00:06:14.065
I’d better go home.

00:06:14.145 --> 00:06:15.465
Hey, wait.

00:06:16.945 --> 00:06:18.265
I want to…

00:06:19.625 --> 00:06:21.265
thank you for earlier…

00:06:22.945 --> 00:06:25.385
even if you were being a meddling jerk.

00:06:26.705 --> 00:06:30.145
Can't you just say
a proper "thank you" for once?

00:06:30.225 --> 00:06:31.585
A proper "thank you?"

00:06:33.625 --> 00:06:34.865
Fine.

00:07:17.425 --> 00:07:18.545
Wait, wait.

00:07:18.625 --> 00:07:19.865
Be careful.

00:07:20.945 --> 00:07:23.105
-Be careful of what?
-These.

00:07:24.065 --> 00:07:25.065
Oh.

00:07:38.825 --> 00:07:40.185
Grandma's sleeping.

00:08:31.385 --> 00:08:32.225
This is Doctor Nabnueng speaking.

00:08:33.425 --> 00:08:37.705
Nabnueng, are you doing well?

00:08:38.985 --> 00:08:39.985
Yes.

00:08:40.065 --> 00:08:41.225
Look…

00:08:41.305 --> 00:08:43.705
I'm not calling to pressure you.

00:08:44.985 --> 00:08:49.185
I just wanted to know
if you have made a decision yet.

00:08:55.065 --> 00:08:58.305
Nabnueng! This is me!

00:09:03.145 --> 00:09:08.865
Nabnueng, you have a younger sister.
Her name is Nene.

00:09:24.265 --> 00:09:28.705
She always said she wants
to be a doctor just like you.

00:09:31.265 --> 00:09:32.465
Yes.

00:09:35.585 --> 00:09:38.625
But I’m here to ask for your help.

00:09:40.505 --> 00:09:43.105
Can you please help your sister?

00:09:44.505 --> 00:09:45.825
Help her?

00:09:47.025 --> 00:09:48.345
What’s wrong with her?

00:09:50.705 --> 00:09:52.665
She has Aplastic Anemia.

00:09:53.345 --> 00:09:56.905
She needs a bone marrow transplant, but…

00:09:59.065 --> 00:10:02.585
It has to come from a full sibling.

00:10:06.265 --> 00:10:08.465
If anything happens to her…

00:10:10.185 --> 00:10:11.705
I can’t go on living.

00:10:15.745 --> 00:10:17.305
Please, help your sister.

00:10:29.185 --> 00:10:31.465
Pi Doc and I can touch each other now.

00:10:31.545 --> 00:10:33.225
What?! Are you really cured?

00:10:33.305 --> 00:10:37.505
Cured or not, but the doctor
asked me to be his boyfriend!

00:10:37.585 --> 00:10:39.945
-What?! Really?!
-Yay!

00:10:40.025 --> 00:10:42.505
-I’m so happy for you.
-Thanks, Lemon.

00:10:42.585 --> 00:10:43.705
We have to celebrate this, right?

00:10:44.385 --> 00:10:45.785
Maybe later?

00:10:45.865 --> 00:10:48.105
My boyfriend just asked me out for dinner.

00:10:50.625 --> 00:10:52.505
Well, I guess it’s just you and me then.

00:10:52.585 --> 00:10:53.385
Oh, gimme a sec.

00:10:54.545 --> 00:10:55.625
Hello?

00:10:55.705 --> 00:10:58.345
Are you in front of the house?
Okay, I'm coming down now.

00:10:58.425 --> 00:11:00.545
Love you too. Bye-bye.

00:11:01.865 --> 00:11:04.225
Were you talking to me?
Soda’s taking me out.

00:11:04.945 --> 00:11:06.105
I’m off.

00:11:06.985 --> 00:11:08.385
See ya.

00:11:09.345 --> 00:11:11.785
Sailom, have you eaten yet?
Want to grab something to eat?

00:11:11.865 --> 00:11:14.425
Sure, Pi Doc! See you soon!

00:11:22.585 --> 00:11:24.585
I'm just background noise again.

00:11:26.305 --> 00:11:28.945
At least I still have my games.

00:11:45.705 --> 00:11:46.625
Pi Doc!

00:11:48.625 --> 00:11:49.985
Is something wrong?

00:11:54.905 --> 00:11:56.945
Just… a little bit.

00:12:00.625 --> 00:12:01.825
Take a deep breath.

00:12:03.785 --> 00:12:05.465
You're here with me now.

00:12:06.025 --> 00:12:08.065
If there's anything bothering you,

00:12:08.145 --> 00:12:10.185
you can tell me.

00:12:13.905 --> 00:12:15.225
I'm just troubled.

00:12:19.745 --> 00:12:22.065
-My birth mother came back.
-What?

00:12:22.785 --> 00:12:23.705
Are you…

00:12:24.665 --> 00:12:27.665
are you okay?

00:12:31.345 --> 00:12:32.745
I’m in a difficult position.

00:12:36.705 --> 00:12:39.145
She said my biological sister is sick

00:12:39.865 --> 00:12:41.385
and needs my help.

00:12:42.225 --> 00:12:43.545
How can you help?

00:12:44.145 --> 00:12:45.665
A bone marrow transplant.

00:12:51.385 --> 00:12:53.385
Will… it be dangerous?

00:12:54.425 --> 00:12:56.465
Is it going to be hard for you?

00:12:56.545 --> 00:12:58.385
What kind of illness is it?

00:12:59.545 --> 00:13:00.985
She has Aplastic Anemia.

00:13:01.705 --> 00:13:03.505
She needs a transplant.

00:13:04.425 --> 00:13:07.105
It has to come from a full
sibling with the same parents.

00:13:08.625 --> 00:13:10.345
Are you going to do it?

00:13:17.025 --> 00:13:18.665
I haven't decided yet.

00:13:26.945 --> 00:13:30.665
I always tell my patients
to listen to their own hearts

00:13:32.505 --> 00:13:34.505
to find out what they truly want,

00:13:36.665 --> 00:13:38.585
so they can solve their issues.

00:13:42.625 --> 00:13:44.985
But when it's my turn

00:13:46.425 --> 00:13:48.465
I have no idea what I want,

00:13:50.305 --> 00:13:52.385
or what I should do.

00:13:53.305 --> 00:13:56.225
I don't even know how…

00:13:56.865 --> 00:13:57.865
I’m…

00:14:01.185 --> 00:14:03.705
supposed to feel.

00:14:06.945 --> 00:14:09.705
The parents who abandoned me at birth

00:14:11.185 --> 00:14:14.025
are now asking me to save a sister.

00:14:28.105 --> 00:14:29.065
Pi Doc.

00:14:33.865 --> 00:14:36.665
No matter what you decide,

00:14:40.465 --> 00:14:41.665
I’m right here with you.

00:15:15.585 --> 00:15:16.585
Right.

00:15:19.105 --> 00:15:20.505
That's right!

00:15:21.145 --> 00:15:22.145
Hey…

00:15:23.265 --> 00:15:24.305
Hey!

00:15:24.825 --> 00:15:27.305
I pay you to serve coffee,
not to shake your asses!

00:15:27.985 --> 00:15:30.025
Chill out! It’s for the shop's page.

00:15:30.105 --> 00:15:32.265
To bring in customers!

00:15:32.345 --> 00:15:34.665
So many people watching.

00:15:35.425 --> 00:15:39.305
All I see is you
thrusting your crotches! Move it!

00:15:39.385 --> 00:15:42.265
Come and help me wash dishes.

00:15:42.345 --> 00:15:43.625
Be careful.

00:15:48.505 --> 00:15:49.785
Old man,

00:15:51.465 --> 00:15:53.425
try this new recipe.

00:15:59.705 --> 00:16:00.865
How is it?

00:16:01.465 --> 00:16:02.385
Good.

00:16:02.465 --> 00:16:03.425
Another bite?

00:16:07.705 --> 00:16:09.105
I knew you'd like it.

00:16:09.185 --> 00:16:13.705
-Ahem…
-Look at you two!

00:16:13.785 --> 00:16:17.465
Is something going on between you two?

00:16:17.545 --> 00:16:19.065
Hiding something?

00:16:20.025 --> 00:16:21.745
-Going to take out the trash?
-Yep.

00:16:21.825 --> 00:16:23.745
Here, let me help you with that.

00:16:24.745 --> 00:16:26.025
What?

00:16:33.665 --> 00:16:34.625
Gimme that.

00:16:35.185 --> 00:16:36.425
Pi DinDin,

00:16:36.505 --> 00:16:40.185
I saw you feeding Pi Tawan.

00:16:40.265 --> 00:16:41.985
Tell me, are you guys dating?

00:16:42.665 --> 00:16:43.865
No! We're nothing!

00:16:43.945 --> 00:16:46.065
Your voice went high.

00:16:46.745 --> 00:16:48.825
We’re nothing.

00:16:48.905 --> 00:16:51.145
You’re acting suspicious.

00:16:51.225 --> 00:16:55.825
I'll show you suspicious! Come here!

00:16:55.905 --> 00:16:58.225
-Get back inside.
-No! Stop!

00:16:58.305 --> 00:17:01.625
You’re not suspicious! Help me!

00:17:02.505 --> 00:17:05.345
Move the drinks to this spot.

00:17:06.585 --> 00:17:07.665
Is it prettier?

00:17:13.025 --> 00:17:14.345
Let’s take a selfie.

00:17:22.065 --> 00:17:23.184
Let see.

00:17:26.025 --> 00:17:27.184
What?

00:17:28.224 --> 00:17:30.745
It looks funny, doesn’t it?

00:17:32.185 --> 00:17:33.905
How is it funny?

00:17:38.625 --> 00:17:40.785
Hey, what was that for?

00:17:44.865 --> 00:17:47.185
Pattaya’s sun is strong recently.

00:17:47.265 --> 00:17:50.385
Oh, yeah. I have this with me.

00:17:50.465 --> 00:17:51.905
Wanna try?

00:17:53.305 --> 00:17:54.185
Yeah.

00:18:25.585 --> 00:18:27.025
You’ll get better soon, sweetie.

00:18:33.345 --> 00:18:34.505
Nabnueng.

00:18:35.785 --> 00:18:38.185
Hello.

00:18:38.265 --> 00:18:39.185
Hi.

00:18:42.185 --> 00:18:46.665
Nabnueng, this is Nene,
your sister I told you about.

00:18:49.625 --> 00:18:51.465
Hello.

00:18:51.545 --> 00:18:52.705
Hello.

00:18:53.625 --> 00:18:58.265
You’re way more handsome than
in the pictures Mom showed me.

00:18:59.465 --> 00:19:01.545
You’re very cute yourself.

00:19:01.625 --> 00:19:03.465
Thank you.

00:19:04.505 --> 00:19:08.105
And… who is this handsome man?

00:19:10.745 --> 00:19:12.065
This is Pi Sailom.

00:19:12.625 --> 00:19:13.905
He’s my boyfriend.

00:19:14.505 --> 00:19:16.265
Nice to meet you.

00:19:21.745 --> 00:19:23.505
How are you doing?

00:19:25.625 --> 00:19:29.545
I’m so bored. I want to go outside,

00:19:29.625 --> 00:19:32.065
but Mom and Dad won't let me.

00:19:32.745 --> 00:19:34.825
You're not fully recovered yet.

00:19:36.025 --> 00:19:39.465
But I’ll be better soon, right?

00:19:39.545 --> 00:19:41.345
Like you guys said?

00:19:44.305 --> 00:19:45.425
Yes.

00:19:47.065 --> 00:19:49.625
When I get better,

00:19:49.705 --> 00:19:52.345
you have to take me to the beach.

00:19:52.425 --> 00:19:55.825
I want to play in the
water and build sandcastles.

00:19:56.425 --> 00:19:59.785
Pi Doctor and Pi Sailom,
you have to come with me, okay?

00:20:07.465 --> 00:20:09.705
-Of course.
-Yay.

00:20:10.745 --> 00:20:14.265
Mom, Pi Doctor
and Pi Sailom will go with me.

00:20:14.345 --> 00:20:15.185
Yes.

00:20:17.545 --> 00:20:20.785
But you must get treated first.

00:20:20.865 --> 00:20:22.585
Yes.

00:20:22.665 --> 00:20:27.105
Is it hard being a doctor?
I want to be one too.

00:20:27.185 --> 00:20:29.505
I want to be cool just like you.

00:20:37.545 --> 00:20:41.705
Yes, you can definitely be a doctor.

00:21:19.185 --> 00:21:20.265
Water for you.

00:21:37.025 --> 00:21:38.785
Nene is really sweet.

00:21:43.225 --> 00:21:45.745
Yeah, she really is.

00:21:54.505 --> 00:21:55.785
I’ve made my decision.

00:22:01.625 --> 00:22:03.385
I’m going to help her.

00:22:09.305 --> 00:22:10.865
I’ve been thinking to myself,

00:22:12.185 --> 00:22:15.265
throughout my career,
I’ve helped so many patients.

00:22:15.865 --> 00:22:19.505
I’ve treated them until
they recovered and could move on.

00:22:22.665 --> 00:22:25.425
If I set aside my personal feelings,

00:22:26.705 --> 00:22:29.545
there’s no reason
why I shouldn't help Nene.

00:22:32.145 --> 00:22:34.265
I’m so proud of you, Pi Doc.

00:22:49.265 --> 00:22:52.345
Micky, don't you think the café’s
been packed every day lately?

00:22:52.425 --> 00:22:54.025
Yeah, I think so too.

00:22:54.705 --> 00:22:57.865
Maybe it’s our TikToks
that are bringing them in?

00:22:59.225 --> 00:23:00.185
I'm heading out.

00:23:00.985 --> 00:23:01.825
Yep.

00:23:01.905 --> 00:23:04.105
PI DinDin! Wait for me!

00:23:04.705 --> 00:23:05.825
Open the door for me.

00:23:05.905 --> 00:23:08.625
Sure. Taking out the trash?

00:23:08.705 --> 00:23:10.625
-Yep.
-Here, let me help.

00:23:11.625 --> 00:23:12.465
Okay.

00:23:15.745 --> 00:23:16.785
Take it all.

00:23:20.785 --> 00:23:21.625
Heave!

00:23:27.625 --> 00:23:28.705
-I’ll take that.
-Okay!

00:23:30.785 --> 00:23:31.745
Okay!

00:23:31.825 --> 00:23:33.785
Thank you, Pi DinDin.

00:23:33.865 --> 00:23:35.585
Sure thing. I'm off then.

00:23:35.665 --> 00:23:38.385
See you tomorrow. Bye-bye.

00:23:38.465 --> 00:23:39.425
Bye-bye.

00:23:42.985 --> 00:23:44.425
-I’m going.
-See yah.

00:23:45.305 --> 00:23:46.865
-Bye!
-Bye-bye.

00:23:58.785 --> 00:23:59.585
-Shut up!
-Let go of me!

00:24:13.465 --> 00:24:15.545
Where did Lookso go?

00:24:15.625 --> 00:24:17.345
Have you seen your sister?

00:24:17.425 --> 00:24:20.225
I just saw her taking out the trash.

00:24:20.305 --> 00:24:21.145
Is she back inside yet?

00:24:21.225 --> 00:24:22.745
Not yet.

00:24:22.825 --> 00:24:26.065
I was washing dishes
in the kitchen and didn't see her.

00:24:26.585 --> 00:24:29.065
I didn't see her either.

00:24:40.545 --> 00:24:42.785
She’s not picking up.

00:24:43.705 --> 00:24:46.145
Everyone, please help me find her.

00:25:30.705 --> 00:25:33.545
If you have a song you would
like to hear, just write it down.

00:25:45.745 --> 00:25:47.505
If you don't send the money,

00:25:48.905 --> 00:25:51.305
I'll film myself cutting
this brat's kidney out.

00:25:51.385 --> 00:25:53.305
-Let me go!!
-and send it to you!

00:25:57.905 --> 00:25:59.625
And don't think about calling the cops.

00:26:00.865 --> 00:26:03.185
You know whose pocket they're in.

00:26:09.625 --> 00:26:11.065
Who the hell are these bastards?

00:26:14.905 --> 00:26:18.625
They… are my loan shark's goons.

00:26:19.665 --> 00:26:21.705
Why the hell did they take Lookso?!

00:26:23.265 --> 00:26:26.425
They want me to pay them back…

00:26:28.265 --> 00:26:29.105
a million baht.

00:26:29.185 --> 00:26:30.105
A million?!

00:26:30.825 --> 00:26:32.465
That much?

00:26:34.105 --> 00:26:37.425
But what did Lookso ever do to them?

00:26:38.985 --> 00:26:41.985
They must have known I work here…

00:26:42.665 --> 00:26:44.625
so they took her to blackmail me.

00:26:53.465 --> 00:26:54.785
Auntie Pailin, I’m sorry.

00:26:56.105 --> 00:26:57.225
I'm so sorry.

00:26:58.225 --> 00:26:59.745
Auntie Pailin, I’m sorry.

00:27:01.185 --> 00:27:02.825
I’m so sorry.

00:27:04.705 --> 00:27:06.025
Please forgive me.

00:27:08.785 --> 00:27:10.385
Then I’m to blame too.

00:27:12.345 --> 00:27:14.985
I stepped in to help DinDin the other day.

00:27:16.145 --> 00:27:19.545
They’re probably getting back at me.

00:27:20.225 --> 00:27:21.945
It’s my fault…

00:27:22.705 --> 00:27:24.945
I failed to protect my daughter.

00:27:26.105 --> 00:27:27.785
Everyone, calm down.

00:27:28.785 --> 00:27:30.545
This is not the time for blame.

00:27:31.465 --> 00:27:35.545
We need to focus on how
to get Lookso back. And quickly.

00:27:37.305 --> 00:27:38.425
DinDin.

00:27:38.505 --> 00:27:39.345
Yes?

00:27:39.425 --> 00:27:41.065
Did they send a location?

00:27:44.585 --> 00:27:45.425
Here.

00:27:46.185 --> 00:27:49.065
They said we must bring the money…

00:27:50.185 --> 00:27:51.345
before 3 a.m.

00:27:52.865 --> 00:27:54.025
3 a.m?

00:27:56.225 --> 00:27:57.945
We only have two hours left.

00:28:14.505 --> 00:28:18.065
This is a hundred thousand in cash.

00:28:18.145 --> 00:28:19.545
Yes, Mom.

00:28:20.145 --> 00:28:21.905
It's all I could find.

00:28:22.585 --> 00:28:23.905
That's okay, Mom.

00:28:23.985 --> 00:28:26.465
I put in three hundred thousand.

00:28:26.545 --> 00:28:27.825
Tawan added a hundred and fifty.

00:28:28.505 --> 00:28:30.265
Plus Mom's hundred thousand

00:28:30.345 --> 00:28:32.025
and Pi Nueng's hundred and fifty.

00:28:33.185 --> 00:28:34.665
The total is seven hundred thousand.

00:28:36.225 --> 00:28:37.305
Oh, no.

00:28:37.385 --> 00:28:39.225
We're still three hundred thousand short.

00:28:39.865 --> 00:28:45.025
It's almost 2 a.m. Where are we
going to find the rest in time?

00:28:49.425 --> 00:28:52.665
Everyone, another message.

00:28:55.545 --> 00:28:56.865
Let me go!!

00:28:56.945 --> 00:28:59.785
Shut up! Or I'll blast your guts out!

00:29:00.825 --> 00:29:03.065
You have less than an hour left.

00:29:03.665 --> 00:29:05.425
If the money isn't here,

00:29:05.505 --> 00:29:06.865
I'm taking this brat's kidney.

00:29:20.625 --> 00:29:24.505
Let me go! Kidnapping for ransom
in this day? So backward!

00:29:25.185 --> 00:29:28.625
Why don't you talk it out?! How can
you use violence against a kid like this?

00:29:29.225 --> 00:29:32.025
How were you even raised?
I don’t want to lecture you,

00:29:32.105 --> 00:29:34.545
but can you act like civilized adults?

00:29:35.105 --> 00:29:38.025
I told you guys to shut her up!

00:29:38.105 --> 00:29:41.905
What kind of brat talks this much?
Is there a motor in her mouth?

00:29:41.985 --> 00:29:44.065
It’s better than being
a rotten adult like you!

00:29:44.145 --> 00:29:45.505
Hold still!

00:29:49.185 --> 00:29:50.345
What time is it?

00:29:51.185 --> 00:29:52.785
Almost 3 a.m, Boss.

00:29:54.185 --> 00:29:56.865
If they aren’t here in ten minutes,

00:29:58.385 --> 00:30:01.625
go get the surgical tools ready.

00:30:28.825 --> 00:30:29.865
Where’s the money?

00:30:31.945 --> 00:30:33.425
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:30:35.425 --> 00:30:38.705
Slow down. Money first.

00:30:40.145 --> 00:30:42.265
A fair trade. Cash for the kid.

00:30:43.345 --> 00:30:44.305
Give it here!

00:30:47.065 --> 00:30:48.785
You said it’s a fair trade.

00:30:50.945 --> 00:30:53.465
So why should I hand over the cash first?

00:30:54.265 --> 00:30:55.665
Untie my sister.

00:30:56.265 --> 00:30:57.825
Bring her to the center.

00:30:58.585 --> 00:31:00.385
I’ll walk to you with the money,

00:31:01.385 --> 00:31:04.585
take my sister,
and you get the cash. Deal?

00:31:04.665 --> 00:31:07.305
How do I know you’re not playing tricks?

00:31:07.385 --> 00:31:08.545
Look at us.

00:31:09.105 --> 00:31:12.305
We’re unarmed and outnumbered.

00:31:12.985 --> 00:31:14.345
You have the upper hand here.

00:31:18.145 --> 00:31:19.745
Untie her.

00:31:28.945 --> 00:31:30.865
Get over here!

00:31:30.945 --> 00:31:32.625
-Pi Nabnueng!
-Hey! Shut it!

00:31:34.465 --> 00:31:38.105
One more word and
I'll shoot your brothers one by one.

00:31:40.185 --> 00:31:42.225
Let DinDin bring the money here.

00:31:42.305 --> 00:31:44.145
It doesn’t matter who brings the money!

00:31:44.225 --> 00:31:45.945
How dare you bargain with me!

00:31:52.585 --> 00:31:53.985
Okay, okay.

00:32:00.905 --> 00:32:01.985
Here you go!

00:32:02.065 --> 00:32:03.225
Put it down!

00:32:03.985 --> 00:32:05.225
Let the kid go first.

00:32:05.945 --> 00:32:08.025
You think you can negotiate?

00:32:09.225 --> 00:32:10.265
Alright!

00:32:14.345 --> 00:32:15.545
For you!!

00:32:16.345 --> 00:32:19.225
-How could you do that?!
-I gotta make sure

00:32:19.825 --> 00:32:21.665
the money is all here.

00:32:22.265 --> 00:32:23.705
Take the money, now!

00:32:25.985 --> 00:32:27.345
Stay still.

00:32:32.465 --> 00:32:33.705
Hey!

00:32:33.785 --> 00:32:35.225
Count every single baht!

00:32:37.825 --> 00:32:38.945
Arg!!

00:32:40.785 --> 00:32:42.385
Ouch!!

00:32:44.825 --> 00:32:46.425
Now we're even.

00:33:01.065 --> 00:33:02.185
Mom!

00:33:02.785 --> 00:33:04.105
Lookso!

00:33:04.905 --> 00:33:07.705
Are you okay, baby? Are you hurt anywhere?

00:33:07.785 --> 00:33:10.185
I'm okay. Everyone came
to save me just in time.

00:33:10.905 --> 00:33:14.625
Thank god, you're safe now.

00:33:17.185 --> 00:33:18.625
Auntie,

00:33:20.025 --> 00:33:23.905
I’m so sorry for causing all this trouble.

00:33:25.065 --> 00:33:27.545
DinDin, it’s okay.

00:33:28.625 --> 00:33:30.465
Let the past be the past.

00:33:30.545 --> 00:33:32.425
The problem is solved.

00:33:33.545 --> 00:33:34.825
Everything is settled.

00:33:43.585 --> 00:33:44.625
Lookso,

00:33:46.145 --> 00:33:47.305
I'm so sorry.

00:33:48.985 --> 00:33:50.465
It’s okay.

00:33:57.865 --> 00:33:59.105
Are you okay, Pi Doc?

00:33:59.185 --> 00:34:00.185
Sailom?

00:34:01.185 --> 00:34:02.145
How did you get here?

00:34:10.465 --> 00:34:12.585
Sky! You okay, man?

00:34:12.665 --> 00:34:15.105
I saw the Boss
and the guys heading out to help you!

00:34:15.185 --> 00:34:16.304
Yeah, I'm fine.

00:34:17.145 --> 00:34:18.865
Good to hear.

00:34:58.465 --> 00:34:59.705
Does it hurt?

00:35:07.945 --> 00:35:09.025
Can I hold your hand?

00:35:14.585 --> 00:35:15.625
Sure.

00:35:43.745 --> 00:35:45.025
Can I touch your cheek?

00:35:50.025 --> 00:35:51.105
Yes.

00:38:24.905 --> 00:38:26.225
If this is too much for you,

00:38:27.385 --> 00:38:28.625
I can stop.

00:38:30.265 --> 00:38:31.465
No, don’t.

00:38:35.145 --> 00:38:36.305
Don’t stop.

00:40:00.065 --> 00:40:03.585
I thought I was dreaming about
someone stealing a kiss from me.

00:40:05.465 --> 00:40:06.905
That wasn’t stealing.

00:40:07.705 --> 00:40:10.705
It’s called a "morning kiss".

00:40:12.425 --> 00:40:13.585
Why?

00:40:14.505 --> 00:40:15.865
Don’t you like it?

00:40:18.705 --> 00:40:19.785
I do.

00:40:21.145 --> 00:40:22.225
A lot.

00:40:24.625 --> 00:40:25.705
What about you?

00:40:27.385 --> 00:40:28.425
Like it?

00:40:31.465 --> 00:40:32.785
I kissed you.

00:40:33.585 --> 00:40:35.425
Of course I like it.

00:40:37.505 --> 00:40:40.425
I’m not talking about the kiss.

00:40:43.425 --> 00:40:44.945
I mean…

00:40:52.465 --> 00:40:54.305
what we did last night.

00:40:54.905 --> 00:40:56.265
Like it?

00:40:58.185 --> 00:40:59.905
-What?
-Answer me.

00:41:02.025 --> 00:41:02.985
W…

00:41:03.065 --> 00:41:05.105
what are you talking about?

00:41:07.225 --> 00:41:08.825
Just answer me.

00:41:09.705 --> 00:41:11.065
Did you like it?

00:41:13.345 --> 00:41:14.185
Come on.

00:41:16.145 --> 00:41:17.665
I just…

00:41:19.465 --> 00:41:23.745
don’t want to be the only one enjoying it.

00:41:25.025 --> 00:41:27.665
I want you to be happy with me.

00:41:30.505 --> 00:41:31.345
Now, answer me.

00:41:37.825 --> 00:41:41.825
I don't remember what we did last night.

00:41:44.625 --> 00:41:47.025
Do you need a memory refresh then?

00:41:57.825 --> 00:41:59.265
Remember now?

00:42:08.745 --> 00:42:10.265
Stop teasing me.

00:42:13.025 --> 00:42:14.305
Just answer me.

00:42:28.745 --> 00:42:29.865
Nabnueng!

00:42:36.825 --> 00:42:38.705
I’ll go wait for you downstairs.

00:42:47.305 --> 00:42:48.265
Hey…

00:42:50.745 --> 00:42:51.905
Nabnueng.

00:42:53.785 --> 00:42:55.025
When did you get back?

00:42:55.585 --> 00:42:57.025
A while ago.

00:42:58.105 --> 00:42:59.945
And I’ve moved back here for good.

00:43:02.785 --> 00:43:05.825
I realized I can't live without you.

00:43:14.305 --> 00:43:15.305
Sailom,

00:43:21.105 --> 00:43:22.425
this is Yanin.

00:43:23.905 --> 00:43:25.585
The ex-girlfriend I told you about.

00:43:26.265 --> 00:43:27.225
Yes.

00:43:28.505 --> 00:43:29.465
Nice to meet you.

00:43:30.665 --> 00:43:31.905
Hello.

00:43:31.985 --> 00:43:33.305
And Yanin,

00:43:35.225 --> 00:43:36.345
this is Sailom.

00:43:41.025 --> 00:43:41.865
My boyfriend.

00:43:48.185 --> 00:43:49.545
But you said you’d wait for me.

00:43:50.945 --> 00:43:52.745
To be honest, I did wait.

00:43:54.025 --> 00:43:55.105
For a very long time.

00:43:57.105 --> 00:43:59.985
But you chose to go
and live your own life.

00:44:01.705 --> 00:44:04.105
I respected your decision.

00:44:07.465 --> 00:44:08.825
And today…

00:44:08.905 --> 00:44:12.505
I’ve made a choice of my own.

00:44:15.945 --> 00:44:18.745
I hope you can respect mine too.

00:44:35.745 --> 00:44:37.065
I should go.

00:45:11.505 --> 00:45:12.625
Are you ready, Pi Doc?

00:45:13.945 --> 00:45:15.105
I'm ready.

00:45:15.785 --> 00:45:17.785
The surgery will take a while.

00:45:21.385 --> 00:45:23.025
You'll get through it just fine.

00:45:24.305 --> 00:45:26.265
I'll be right here by your side.

00:45:26.345 --> 00:45:27.785
Don't be afraid, okay?

00:45:30.665 --> 00:45:32.665
Thank you so much, Sailom.

00:45:33.425 --> 00:45:34.785
Thank you for staying with me.

00:45:37.345 --> 00:45:38.465
Always.

00:46:05.825 --> 00:46:08.785
Hurry up and graduate.
Have some pity on the guy over there.

00:46:09.385 --> 00:46:12.065
You won't go back to being
a pilot because of that kid?

00:46:12.145 --> 00:46:13.305
You brat!

00:46:13.385 --> 00:46:14.945
I told you to stay out of my business!

00:46:15.025 --> 00:46:18.105
If punching me makes
you feel better, go ahead.

00:46:18.185 --> 00:46:20.705
He's been staring at his phone
and moping like this for a week now.

00:46:20.785 --> 00:46:23.185
It’s like when he broke up with Pi Yanin.

00:46:23.265 --> 00:46:26.065
Still overthinking? I'm pretty
sure Pi Doc is over his ex by now.

00:46:26.145 --> 00:46:27.185
I wouldn't be so sure.

00:46:27.265 --> 00:46:29.665
Some people still
can't let go of the old one.

00:46:29.745 --> 00:46:33.225
When you told your ex
that I was your boyfriend,

00:46:33.305 --> 00:46:34.785
did you really mean it? Or…